Post SpanishAmerican War
After the war, Indiana returned to training exercises with the North Atlantic Squadron. In May 1900, she and Massachusetts were placed in the reserve fleet as the navy had an acute officer shortage and needed to take the new Kearsarge class battleship Kearsarge and  Illinois class battleships into commission.Cite news
